OL,5, Energy suppliers have been warned they 
OL,6, should retain profits rather than pay  
OL,7, out returns to shareholders, to ensure 
OL,8, firms can weather future price shocks. 
OL,10,FRegulator Ofgem said firms "must learn 
OL,11,Fthe lessons of the energy crisis",     
OL,12,Fadding "a return to the practices we   
OL,13,Fsaw before isn't on the table".        
OL,15,FSome 30 suppliers have gone bust since 
OL,16,Fenergy prices started to rise in 2021. 
OL,18,FHigher wholesale gas prices, driven by 
OL,19,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine, made     
OL,20,Fprice deals to customers undeliverable.
